title: Dozens killed in alleged Syrian chemical attack
text:
Dozens killed in alleged Syrian chemical attack 5:03pm IST - 01:44 
At least 49 people are reported to have been killed in an alleged chemical weapons attack on the rebel-held Syrian city of Douma. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
